{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-024","title":"Sentence 24","sectionId":"sentences-021","sectionTitle":"Sentence 21-30","pageStart":170,"pageEnd":175,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":51,"duplicateEntryCount":1,"pages":[{"number":170,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 24"},{"type":"text","text":"Out in remote areas of the countryside, in rural locations, music was"},{"type":"text","text":"more traditional; the same songs were enjoyed by previous generations."},{"type":"text","text":"在遥远偏僻的乡村，在农村地区，音乐更传统；同样的歌曲，"},{"type":"text","text":"几代人都在听。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是“Music was more traditional; the same songs were"},{"type":"text","text":"enjoyed”。句首“out in remote ... rural locations”是地点状语。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"remote /rɪˈmoʊt/ a. 偏僻的，遥远的","headword":"remote"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 remote mountain area 偏远山区"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 distant a. 遥远的"},{"type":"entry","text":"rural /ˈrʊrəl/ a. 乡村的，农村的","headword":"rural"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 rur（乡村）+al（…的）→乡村的"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 ruralize vt. 使农村化 vi. 在农村居住"},{"type":"text","text":"rurality n. 农村景色"},{"type":"entry","text":"location /loʊˈkeɪʃn/ n. 位置；场所","headword":"location"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 loc（地方）+ation→位置；场所"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 locality n. 地点；位置"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 locate vt. 定位"}]},{"number":171,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"previous /ˈpriːviəs/ a. 先的，在前的","headword":"previous"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 pre（前）+vi（路）+ous（…的）→前面的路→以前的"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 former a. 从前的"},{"type":"text","text":"preceding a. 在前的"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 previously ad. 先前，以前"},{"type":"entry","text":"generation /ˌdʒenəˈreɪʃn/ n. 一代（人）；产生，发生","headword":"generation"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 gener（出生）+ation（表名词）→一代一代的人出生→一代"},{"type":"text","text":"（人）"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 for generations 几代人"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"“流行乐与民谣”相关词："},{"type":"text","text":"absolute music 纯音乐"},{"type":"entry","text":"blues /bluːz/ n. 蓝调音乐；布鲁斯","headword":"blues"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 country blues 乡村蓝调；乡村布鲁斯"},{"type":"text","text":"country music 乡村音乐"},{"type":"entry","text":"country-folk /ˈkʌntrifoʊk/ n. 乡村民谣","headword":"country-folk"},{"type":"entry","text":"country-pop /ˈkʌntripɑːp/ n. 乡村流行乐","headword":"country-pop"},{"type":"text","text":"electric blues 电子蓝调；电子布鲁斯"},{"type":"text","text":"folk jazz 民谣爵士"},{"type":"text","text":"folk music 民谣"}]},{"number":172,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"funk /fʌŋk/ n. 乡土爵士乐","headword":"funk"},{"type":"entry","text":"hip-hop /ˈhɪphɑːp/ n. 嘻哈音乐","headword":"hip-hop"},{"type":"text","text":"instrumental music 器乐"},{"type":"entry","text":"jazz /dʒæz/ n. 爵士乐 vt. 使活泼","headword":"jazz"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 jazz band 爵士乐队"},{"type":"text","text":"jazz blues 爵士蓝调；爵士布鲁斯"},{"type":"text","text":"latin rap 拉丁说唱"},{"type":"entry","text":"percussion /pərˈkʌʃn/ n. 打击乐器；敲击","headword":"percussion"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 percussion instrument 打击乐器"},{"type":"text","text":"pop music 流行音乐"},{"type":"entry","text":"punk /pʌŋk/ n. 朋克乐","headword":"punk"},{"type":"text","text":"R&B （rhythm & blues） /ˌɑːr ən ˈbiː/ abbr. 节奏蓝调，节奏布鲁斯"},{"type":"entry","text":"rap /ræp/ n. 说唱音乐","headword":"rap"}]},{"number":173,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 pop rap 流行说唱"},{"type":"text","text":"rock and roll 摇滚乐"},{"type":"entry","text":"soul /soʊl/ n. 灵魂音乐","headword":"soul"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 soul jazz 灵魂爵士"},{"type":"text","text":"traditional folk 传统民谣"},{"type":"text","text":"与“音乐、音乐史”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"album /ˈælbəm/ n. 专辑","headword":"album"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 debut album 首张专辑"},{"type":"entry","text":"chorus /ˈkɔːrəs/ n. 合唱，合唱曲；副歌","headword":"chorus"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 chorus master 合唱队指挥"},{"type":"entry","text":"composition /ˌkɑːmpəˈzɪʃn/ n. 作曲","headword":"composition"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 musical composit